					<head>Commentary</head>
					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597" rend="visible">
						<summary>A fragment of Judeo-Arabic commentary of Japheth ben Ali ha-Levi on Deuteronomy.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="jrb">Hebrew, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
						<msItem rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
							<locus from="1r" to="79v"/>
							<title xml:lang="en">Perush Devarim </title>
							<title xml:lang="he">פרוש דברים</title>
							<note>
								<p>The commentary on Deut. 1:39-2:14, 19:20-22:2, 28:12-20, 35-53.</p>
								<p>The unpointed text of Deut. 1:40-2:15, 19:21-22:3, 28:13-20, 36-55 is embodied, followed by the Arabic translation.</p>
							</note>
							<author key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961">
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="en">Japheth ben Ali, ha-Levi,‏ active 10th century </persName>
								<persName key="http://viaf.org/viaf/54984961" xml:lang="he">יפת בן עלי, הלוי</persName>
							</author>
						</msItem>
					</msContents>
					<physDesc rend="visible">
						<p>Paper codex of the 15th century.</p>
						<objectDesc form="codex">
							<supportDesc material="chart">
								<support>Paper codex. </support>
								<extent>79 folios<dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
										<height>189</height>
										<width>135</width>
									</dimensions>
									<dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
										<height>140</height>
										<width>110</width>
									</dimensions>
								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>79 folios (+ 2 paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>8 quires, of mostly 10 leaves each. The last quire is imperfect.</p>
									<p>Quires signed with Hebrew letters and Arabic words on the upper margin of the first page, and with Hebrew letters on the lower margin of the last page.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Imperfect at the end.</p>
								</condition>
							</supportDesc>
							<layoutDesc>
								<layout columns="1" ruledLines="15" writtenLines="15">
									<p>The Hebrew biblical text is embodied.</p>
								</layout>
							</layoutDesc>
						</objectDesc>
